01:03.148 --> 01:05.042
went to number five

01:01.250 --> 01:05.042
in Finland.

01:05.083 --> 01:06.626
- To this day,
- I can still get

01:06.667 --> 01:08.001
Free stuffed herring

01:08.002 --> 01:09.334
anywhere in Helsinki.

01:11.500 --> 01:13.564
But that does not

01:13.565 --> 01:15.626
explain the hedgehog

01:11.500 --> 01:15.626
on your head.

