Back then

01:16.856 --> 01:18.042
I was called

01:15.667 --> 01:18.042
"the Hair."

01:18.083 --> 01:19.167
This is what my fans

01:19.168 --> 01:20.250
want to see.

01:20.292 --> 01:22.106
Trust me,

01:22.107 --> 01:23.918
nobody wants

01:20.292 --> 01:23.918
to see that.

01:23.959 --> 01:25.042
- I better
- put this away,

01:25.083 --> 01:27.059
- So it doesn't get messed up
- before the show tonight.

01:27.083 --> 01:28.105
Also, it might want

01:28.106 --> 01:29.125
to run on its

01:27.083 --> 01:29.125
exercise wheel.

