♪ First time I saw you

21:07.710 --> 21:09.083
on the street

21:09.125 --> 21:10.439
♪ You looked at me

21:10.440 --> 21:11.751
so warm and sweet

21:11.792 --> 21:13.064
♪ Frothed me up

21:13.065 --> 21:14.334
like a fine souffle

21:14.375 --> 21:16.792
♪ Then brought me down, baby

21:16.834 --> 21:17.876
♪ Don't go!

21:17.918 --> 21:19.709
♪ No matter how I tried

21:19.751 --> 21:21.059
- Is that one
- "the Heartbreaker"?

21:21.083 --> 21:22.244
- More like
- the hip-breaker.

21:23.083 --> 21:25.334
♪ Can't take any more of you

21:25.375 --> 21:27.417
♪ Even with gravy

21:27.459 --> 21:28.500
♪ So dry!

21:28.542 --> 21:31.042
♪ This is the brand new me

21:31.083 --> 21:33.584
♪ Don't mean your fricassee

21:33.626 --> 21:35.751
♪ I'm burned but I am free

21:35.792 --> 21:37.397
♪ No more grill marks

21:37.398 --> 21:39.000
on my heart ♪

