21:44.083 --> 21:45.542
(LAUGHING)

21:46.751 --> 21:48.584
- Thank you,
- Central Park!

21:51.125 --> 21:52.918
- I'm so happy
- for Bertram!

21:52.959 --> 21:54.250
Me too!

21:54.292 --> 21:55.585
And I actually

21:55.586 --> 21:56.876
enjoyed the concert.

21:56.918 --> 21:58.397
Although,

21:58.398 --> 21:59.876
Bertram's crowd surfing

21:56.918 --> 21:59.876
was rather unpleasant.

