You are all

22:21.272 --> 22:22.542
my disciples!

22:22.584 --> 22:24.188
And I...

22:24.189 --> 22:25.792
I'm a golden god!

22:27.000 --> 22:28.042
Wow.

22:28.083 --> 22:29.959
- I think we built up
- his confidence

22:30.000 --> 22:31.063
A little

22:31.064 --> 22:32.125
too much.

22:32.167 --> 22:33.480
Oh, no! He's gonna

22:33.481 --> 22:34.792
crowd surf again!

22:34.834 --> 22:36.083
Run!

22:36.125 --> 22:38.042
- (THUDDING)
- (GLASS BREAKING)

22:38.083 --> 22:39.522
JESSIE: So,

